No. 11-341 (R46-007). Qwest Services Corporation, et al., Petitioners v. Andrew Blood, et al. 565 U.S. 1152, 132 S. Ct. 1087,

181 L. Ed. 2d 805,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 581. January 12, 2012.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Colorado in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 252 P.3d 1071.
